div.p:
Subsemnatul declar ca:
Adeverinta medicala pentru inscrierea in colectivitate - eliberata de catre medicul de familie;
Aviz epidemiologic pentru (re)intrare in colectivitate. Acesta este obligatoriu a fi prezentat:
dupa o perioada de absenta din colectivitate de cel putin 3 zile consecutive;
la plecarea in tabere, etc.
Adeverinta/Fisa medicala cuprinzand: antecedentele fiziolo-gice, principalele antecedente patologice (inclusiv infecto-contagioase), precum si imunizarile efectuate;
Orice alt document si/sau informatie medicala solicitata de catre personalul Verita in conformitate cu Manualul Verita si/sau Sectiunea II - Termeni si Conditii Generale - Art. 9 - asistenta medicala. Administrarea de medicamente elevilor de catre personalul Verita.

I hereby declare that:
Medical certificate approving enrollment into the school setting – issued by the family doctor;
Epidemiological certificate for re(entry) into the school setting. This is mandatory:
after a period of absence from the school setting of at least 3 consecutive days;
upon departure for school trips, etc.
Medical record/certificate that contains: physiological history, the main pathology history (including infection-contagious history) as well as the immunization record;
Any other document and/or medical information requested by the Verita personnel pursuant to the Verita Manual and/or Section II – General Terms and Conditions – Art. 9 – Medical Assistance. The administration of medication to students by Verita personnel.
